widgets_values: The image is a portrait of a young woman standing on a sandy beach. She is wearing a white t-shirt with a plunging neckline and black shorts. Her hair is styled in loose waves and she is looking off to the side with a serious expression on her face. The sky is blue with white clouds and the ocean can be seen in the background. There are palm trees on the left side of the image and the sand is a light beige color.
